<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ النازعات<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٨ص١٠٨:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {يَوْمَ تَرْجُفُ الرَّاجِفَةُ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> تَتْبَعُهَا الرَّادِفَةُ <span class="c2">(٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[النازعات: ٦، ٧]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{الرَّاجِفَةُ}</span>: <span class="c2">«النَّفْخَةُ الأُولَى»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَ <span class="c3">{الرَّادِفَةُ}</span>: <span class="c2">«النَّفْخَةُ الثَّانِيَةُ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>